        "message": "LU-10257 clio: remove unused lock and page layers\n\nMove lpg_index from struct lov_page_slice to struct cl_page and rename\nit cp_comp_index. Remove the then unused struct vvp_lock, lov_page,\nlovsub_lock and lovsub_page, omitting these layers from the\ncorresponding cl_lock or cl_page.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I4dcb0ea186331b4c762d2a4fb7962beaafc88f7e\n"
